doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='Landscaping and sweeping services')
        meta(name='author', content='American Facility Sources')
        title American Facility Sources
        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.3.0/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')
        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Catamaran:100,200,300,400,500,600,700,800,900' rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,100i,300,300i,400,400i,700,700i,900,900i' rel='stylesheet')
        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')
    body#page-top
        // Navigation
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark.fixed-top
            .container.px-5
                a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top') AMERICAN FACILITY SOURCES
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    span.navbar-toggler-icon
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#about') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#services') Services
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#contact') Contact
        // Header
        header.masthead.text-center.text-white(style="background: url('assets/img/cr=w_1240,h_620.webp') no-repeat center center; background-size: cover; height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;")
            .overlay(style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;")
                .masthead-content
                    .container.px-5
                        h1.masthead-heading.mb-0 Landscaping &
                        h2.masthead-subheading.mb-0 Sweeping parking lots
                        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.rounded-pill.mt-5(href='#about') Learn More
        // About Section
        section#about.py-5.bg-light.text-center
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-8
                        h2.display-4 About Us
                        p
                            | American Facility Sources is dedicated to providing top-notch landscaping and sweeping services. With years of experience and a team of skilled professionals, we are committed to enhancing the beauty and functionality of your outdoor spaces. Our mission is to deliver exceptional service that exceeds your expectations.
                        p.highlighted
                            | Now Serving Middle/West Tennessee, Mississippi, Arkansas, Kentucky, Alabama
        // Services Section - Landscaping
        section#services.py-5
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/cr=w_365,h_365.webp', alt='Landscaping Service')
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Landscaping
                            p
                                | Discover the transformative power of professional landscaping by partnering with us. Imagine stepping into a picturesque oasis right in your own backyard—a place where you can unwind, entertain, and connect with nature. With our expertise, dedication, and passion for creating breathtaking landscapes, we will turn that vision into a reality that exceeds your expectations.
        // Services Section - Sweeping
        section#sweeping.py-5.bg-light
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/qt=q_65.webp', alt='Sweeping Service')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Sweeping parking lots
                            p
                                | Partner with American Facility Source today and experience the difference we can make in optimizing your facility's functionality, cleanliness, and overall appeal. Our dedicated team is ready to create a tailored solution that exceeds your expectations and helps your business thrive.
        // Contact Section
        section#contact.py-5
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/ContactUs.jpg', alt='Contact Us')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Contact Us
                            p
                                | Contact us now for a consultation and let us demonstrate how American Facility Source can be your trusted partner in achieving an exceptional facility environment. Together, we'll elevate your space to new heights of excellence.
                            p
                                | Operation Manager: Moe Gaad
                                br
                                | Humboldt, TN
                                br
                                | Phone: (731) 618-2757
        // Footer
        footer.py-5.bg-dark
            .container.px-5
                p.m-0.text-center.text-white.small Copyright © 2024 American Facility Sources - All Rights Reserved.
        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/docs/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')
        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')

    // CSS for highlighting the statement
    style.
        .highlighted {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6347; // You can adjust the color as needed
        }
